object.script:
function onTick()
inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed1 = input.getBool(1)
isPressingRectL = isPressed1 and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 37, h-10, 8, 8) isPressingRectR = isPressed1 and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 50, h-10, 8, 8) isPressingRectU = isPressed1 and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 13, h-10, 8, 8) isPressingRectD = isPressed1 and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 25, h-10, 8, 8)
isPressingRectZOut = isPressed1 and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 74, h-10, 8, 8) isPressingRectZIn = isPressed1 and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 62, h-10, 8, 8)
output.setBool(1, isPressingRectL) output.setBool(2, isPressingRectR) output.setBool(3, isPressingRectU) output.setBool(4, isPressingRectD) output.setBool(5, isPressingRectZIn) output.setBool(6, isPressingRectZOut) end
-- Returns true if the point (x, y) is inside the rectangle at (rectX, rectY) with width rectW and height rectH function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() end

object.script:
function onTick() Zoom = ((input.getNumber(1)) - 0) * ((2) - (96-2)) / (1 - 0) + (96-2)
Down = input.getBool(1) Up = input.getBool(2) Left = input.getBool(3) Right = input.getBool(4) ZOut = input.getBool(5) ZIn = input.getBool(6) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() cw = w/2 ch = h/2 screen.setColor(9, 255, 0)
screen.drawLine(w-1, 2, w-1, h-2) screen.drawLine(w-1, 2, w-4, 2) screen.drawLine(w-1, h-2, w-4, h-2) screen.drawLine(w-1, ch, w-4, ch)
screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawLine(w-1, Zoom, w-4, Zoom)
if Up == true then screen.setColor(33, 33, 64) screen.drawRectF(14, h-9, 7, 7) end
if Down == true then screen.setColor(33, 33, 64) screen.drawRectF(26, h-9, 7, 7) end
if Left == true then screen.setColor(33, 33, 64) screen.drawRectF(38, h-9, 7, 7) end
if Right == true then screen.setColor(33, 33, 64) screen.drawRectF(51, h-9, 7, 7) end
if ZIn == true then screen.setColor(33, 33, 64) screen.drawRectF(63, h-9, 7, 7) end
if ZOut == true then screen.setColor(33, 33, 64) screen.drawRectF(75, h-9, 7, 7) end
screen.setColor(68, 68, 128)
screen.drawRect(13, h-10, 8, 8) --Up screen.drawLine(17, h-7, 14, h-4) screen.drawLine(17, h-7, 20, h-4)
screen.drawRect(25, h-10, 8, 8) --Down screen.drawLine(27, h-7, 30, h-4) screen.drawLine(31, h-7, 28, h-4)
screen.drawRect(37, h-10, 8, 8) --Left screen.drawTextBox(40, h-8, 6, 7, "<")
screen.drawRect(50, h-10, 8, 8) --Right screen.drawTextBox(53, h-8, 6, 7, ">")
screen.drawRect(62, h-10, 8, 8) --Zoom In screen.drawLine(64, h-6, 69, h-6) screen.drawLine(66, h-8, 66, h-3)
screen.drawRect(74, h-10, 8, 8) --Zoom Out screen.drawLine(76, h-6, 81, h-6)
end

function onTick() Zoom = input.getNumber(1) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(9, 255, 0)
screen.drawRect((w/2)-10, (h/2)-10, 20, 20) screen.drawLine((w/2)-10, h/2, (w/2)+10 , h/2) screen.drawLine(w/2, (h/2)-10, w/2 , (h/2)+10)
screen.drawRect((w/2)-10, (h/2)+10, 6, 6) screen.drawRect((w/2)+4, (h/2)+10, 6, 6)
screen.drawLine((w/2)-8, (h/2)+13, (w/2)-5, (h/2)+13) screen.drawLine((w/2)+6, (h/2)+13, (w/2)+9, (h/2)+13) screen.drawLine((w/2)+7, (h/2)+12, (w/2)+7, (h/2)+15)
end

object.script:
-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() RPS = input.getNumber(1) DAG = input.getNumber(2)
VTOL = input.getBool(1)
if VTOL == true then Pitch = 0
elseif VTOL == false and RPS > 9 and DAG < 5 then Pitch = 0
elseif VTOL == false and RPS < 30 then Pitch = -1 end
output.setNumber(1,Pitch)
end

object.script:
function round(num, numdec) local multi = 10^(numdec or 0) return math.floor(num * multi + 0.5) / multi end
function onTick()
Speed = math.floor(input.getNumber(1)) Alt = math.floor(input.getNumber(2)) Fuel = ((input.getNumber(3) - 0) * ((-20) - 0)) / (410 - 0) + 0 P_tilt = (input.getNumber(4)*4)*90 R_tilt = (input.getNumber(5)*4)*90 Compas = math.floor(input.getNumber(6)) Throttle = ((input.getNumber(7) - 0.08) * (25 - (-23))) / (0.5 - 0.08) + (-23) EngRPM = math.floor((input.getNumber(8)*60)) MotorThrottle = ((input.getNumber(9) - (-1)) * (25 - (-23))) / (1 - (-1)) + (-23)
Overspeed = input.getBool(1) VTOL = input.getBool(2) end
function onDraw() w = 288 h = 160 rad = 25
RAlt = round(Alt, -2)
screen.setColor(9, 255, 0)
cw = w/2 --Artificial horizon ch = h/2
Pitch = math.acos(P_tilt / 90) Roll = math.rad(90-R_tilt)
Hx1 = cw + rad * math.cos(Roll + Pitch) Hy1 = ch + rad * math.sin(Roll + Pitch) Hx2 = cw + rad * math.cos(Roll - Pitch) Hy2 = ch + rad * math.sin(Roll - Pitch)
if Speed > 100 and VTOL == false then screen.drawLine(Hx1, Hy1, Hx2, Hy2) screen.drawCircle(cw, ch, 2) screen.drawLine(cw, ch-2, cw, ch-6) screen.drawLine(cw-5, ch, cw-2, ch) screen.drawLine(cw+5, ch, cw+2, ch) elseif VTOL == true then screen.drawLine(Hx1, Hy1, Hx2, Hy2) screen.drawTextBox(cw-23, h-15, 46, 7, "VTOL MODE") end
screen.drawTextBox(2, ch-25, 18, 7, Speed+3) screen.drawTextBox(2, ch-18, 18, 7, Speed+2) screen.drawTextBox(2, ch-11, 18, 7, Speed+1) screen.drawRect(0, ch-5, 18, 8) screen.drawTextBox(2, ch-3, 18, 7, Speed)
if Speed > 1 then screen.drawTextBox(2, ch+5, 18, 7, Speed-1) end
if Speed > 2 then screen.drawTextBox(2, ch+12, 18, 7, Speed-2) end
if Speed > 3 then screen.drawTextBox(2, ch+19, 18, 7, Speed-3) end
screen.drawTextBox(w-22, ch-25, 23, 7, string.format("%#4d", RAlt+300)) screen.drawTextBox(w-22, ch-18, 23, 7, string.format("%#4d", RAlt+200)) screen.drawTextBox(w-22, ch-11, 23, 7, string.format("%#4d", RAlt+100)) screen.drawRect(w-24, ch-5, 23, 8) screen.drawTextBox(w-22, ch-3, 23, 7, string.format("%#4d", Alt))
if RAlt > 100 then screen.drawTextBox(w-22, ch+5, 23, 7, string.format("%#4d", RAlt-100)) end if RAlt > 200 then screen.drawTextBox(w-22, ch+12, 23, 7, string.format("%#4d", RAlt-200)) end if RAlt > 300 then screen.drawTextBox(w-22, ch+19, 23, 7, string.format("%#4d", RAlt-300)) end
screen.drawTextBox(cw-7, 1, 20, 7, Compas)
if VTOL == false then screen.drawLine(23, ch-13, 23, ch+25) if Throttle > 13 then screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawRectF(21, ch-Throttle, 5, 2) else screen.drawRectF(21, ch-Throttle, 5, 2) end screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawLine(23, ch-25, 23, ch-13) --Throttle red line else screen.drawLine(23, ch-25, 23, ch+25) screen.drawRectF(21, ch-MotorThrottle, 5, 2)
end
if Overspeed == true then screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawRect(cw-28, 8, 54, 8) screen.drawTextBox( cw-27, 10, 55, 7,"!OverSpeed!" ) end
screen.setColor(9, 255, 0) screen.drawTextBox(16, ch+27, 23, 7, EngRPM)
screen.drawRect(w-9, h-23, 7, 21) if Fuel > -4 then screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawRectF(w-8, h-2, 6, Fuel) else screen.drawRectF(w-8, h-2, 6, Fuel) end
screen.setColor(9, 255, 0) screen.drawTextBox(w-30, h-6, 21, 7, "Fuel")
end

function onTick() DAG = math.floor(input.getNumber(1)) Alt = math.floor(input.getNumber(2)) Battery = (math.floor(input.getNumber(3)*10000))/100 Speed = math.floor(input.getNumber(4)) RPS = math.floor(input.getNumber(5)) Signal = (math.floor(input.getNumber(6)*10000))/100
Ignition = input.getBool(1) InfraredMode = input.getBool(2) GimbalStab = input.getBool(3) AltHold = input.getBool(4) GearSet = input.getBool(5) Brakes = input.getBool(6) VTOL = input.getBool(7)
if RPS < 1 then RPSLow = true else RPSLow = false end
if DAG > 30 then DAGH = true else DAGH = false end
if Speed < 10 then SpeedL = true SpeedH = false end if Speed > 140 then SpeedL = false SpeedH = true end if (Speed > 10) and (Speed < 140)then SpeedL = false SpeedH = false end
if GearSet == true and RPSLow == true and DAGH == false and SpeedL == true and SpeedH == false then Gear = true elseif GearSet == true and RPSLow == false and DAGH == true and SpeedL == false and SpeedH == true then Gear = true else Gear = false end
if GearSet == true and RPSLow == false and DAGH == false then Gear = false GearAlrm = true else GearAlrm = false end
output.setBool(1, Gear )
end
function onDraw() w = 288 h = 160 cw = w/2 ch = h/2 screen.setColor(9, 255, 0)
if AltHold == true then screen.drawTextBox(cw-17, h-7, 50, 7,"Alt HLD") end
screen.drawTextBox(3, 3, 20, 7, "BAT:") screen.drawTextBox(24, 3, 25, 7, Battery)
screen.drawTextBox(3, 11, 35, 7, "SIGNAL:") screen.drawTextBox(37, 11, 25, 7, Signal)
if Gear == true then screen.drawRect( w-13, 2, 4, 4) screen.drawRectF(w-12, 3, 3, 1) screen.drawRect( w-17, 9, 4, 4) screen.drawRectF(w-16, 10, 3, 1) screen.drawRect( w-9, 9, 4, 4) screen.drawRectF(w-8, 10, 3, 1) else screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawRect( w-13, 2, 4, 4) screen.drawRectF(w-12, 5, 3, 1) screen.drawRect( w-17, 9, 4, 4) screen.drawRectF(w-16, 12, 3, 1) screen.drawRect( w-9, 9, 4, 4) screen.drawRectF(w-8, 12, 3, 1) end
if Brakes == false then screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawTextBox(5, h-9, 30, 7, "Brakes") end
if GearAlrm == true then screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawTextBox(cw-27, ch+9, 60, 7, "Alt Too Low") end
if (Speed < 130) and (Alt > 200) then screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawTextBox(cw-12, ch+9, 25, 7, "Stall") end
if Signal < 25 then screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawRect(cw-33, 8, 60, 8) screen.drawTextBox( cw-32, 10, 70, 7,"!Signal Low!") end
if VTOL == true and Battery < 94 then screen.setColor(255, 16, 0) screen.drawRect(cw-35, 8, 64, 8) screen.drawTextBox( cw-32, 10, 70, 7,"!Battrey Low!") end
end
